<section class="grid place-items-center">
  <div class="lg:mx-56 xl:mx-96 bg-white rounded-3xl">
    <h2 class="text-5xl text-teal-800 font-bold my-5 py-5 mx-4 md:mx-6">
      What is PotLuck?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-teal-900 text-lg mx-4 md:mx-6 mb-10 pb-10 border-b border-teal-400">
        PotLuck is a food-service app created by four
        junior programmers to add a new take on the online
        food ordering industry. PotLuck is unique in that
        it's users can donate any amount of money to add to
        the PotLuck's pool. Then PotLuck will use that donated
        money to pay for another users meal. The idea came from
        the pay-it-forwards that typically happen when a generous
        individual will pay for the cars order behind them in a
        drive-thru. Join PotLuck today and help the hungry in local
        area today!
    </p>
    <p class="text-teal-900 text-center font-bold text-lg md:mx-6 mb-6">
      Get started by using the buttons below to donate or place an order!
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 md:gap-4 mb-6 pb-4">
      <button onclick="window.location.href='/donate';" id="donateBtn" class="button col-span-1 mx-8 w-full md:w-52 bg-teal-600 py-6 text-center inline-block px-6 py-2.5 text-white font-medium text-md leading-tight uppercase
          rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-teal-700 hover:shadow-lg focus:bg-blue-700 focus:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:bg-blue-800 active:shadow-lg transition duration-150 ease-in-out">Donate</button>
      <button onclick="window.location.href='/order';" id="orderBtn" class="button col-span-1 mx-8 w-full md:w-52 bg-teal-600 py-6 text-center inline-block px-6 py-2.5 text-white font-medium text-md leading-tight uppercase
          rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-teal-700 hover:shadow-lg focus:bg-blue-700 focus:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:bg-blue-800 active:shadow-lg transition duration-150 ease-in-out">Order</button>
    </div>    
  </div>
</section>
